HEADWORD: Anostraca
<hw>Anostraca</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>An order of small aquatic
crustaceans lacking a carapace, including the fairy shrimps and the
brine shrimps.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> order <ord>Anostraca</ord>.</syn>⟦br⟧
